data.description: Spacious ranch offering multiple living areas! Living room features hardwood floors and charming built-in shelves. Kitchen boasts maple cabinets, great counter space, breakfast bar, and range plus additional cooktop. Dining room boasts a fireplace. Rear family room provides enough space for multiple functions. Separate office/bonus room. Large sunroom overlooks the beautiful backyard. Two bedroom suites each with a private bath. Third bedroom with hardwood floors. Oversized 2 car garage with exceptional storage or workshop space. Large fenced yard with storage shed, patio and garden.
